Remarks. Some specimens in Pisica’s collection were misidentified as “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C044D63FFF4FF84B3780A52FE9332CD" baseAuthorityName="Kriechbaumer" baseAuthorityYear="1887" class="Insecta" family="Ichneumonidae" genus="Exeristes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="13" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="arundinis">
